tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE training_progress (
    progress_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name TEXT,
    epoch INT,
    loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE neural_networks (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    network_name VARCHAR(50),
    training_start_time TIMESTAMP,
    training_end_time TIMESTAMP,
    training_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE loss_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    network_id INT,
    epoch_number INT,
    loss_value FLOAT,
    validation_loss FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (network_id) REFERENCES neural_networks(id)
);

CREATE TABLE accuracy_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    network_id INT,
    epoch_number INT,
    accuracy FLOAT,
    validation_accuracy FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (network_id) REFERENCES neural_networks(id)
);

CREATE TABLE optimization_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    network_id INT,
    optimization_duration INT,
    optimizer_used VARCHAR(50),
    learning_rate FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (network_id) REFERENCES neural_networks(id)
);

CREATE TABLE NeuralNetworkModel (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR,
    training_start_date TIMESTAMP,
    training_end_date TIMESTAMP,
    loss FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE TrainingLog (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    log_message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE OptimizationLog (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    optimization_message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ErrorLog (
    error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    log_id INT,
    error_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    error_message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Hyperparameters (
    hyperparameters_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    learning_rate FLOAT,
    batch_size INT
)
